    answer: "The default IP address of our cameras is 192.168.1.13 with DHCP enabled by default. To modify: 1. Access the device's web interface. 2. Go to【Network】>【TCP/IP Settings】. 3. Choose between DHCP (automatic IP assignment) or static IP mode. 4. For static IP, enter the desired IP address, subnet mask, and gateway. 5. Configure DNS servers if needed. 6. Save and reboot the device. For enterprise networks, you may also configure VLAN settings, QoS parameters, and port forwarding rules in this section."
